metadata.name: Shiny Fianita #1
metadata.description:
"Clear Fianite or Cubic zirconia"

 Although fianite is an artificial gemstone, it is also the most unique because it has no analogues in the world. 
 Fianite was created by the staff of the Physical Institute of the Academy of Sciences (FIAN) in 1970. The aim of its development was to get the perfect stone for laser
